<section sectnbr = "4C">
<servcat sctnbr = "04" scnbr = "03">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AHRAP70A4306006" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "03" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Pregled diska stražnje kočnice
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AHRAP70A4306005">Uklanjanje i ugradnja diska stražnje kočnice</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Specijalnim alatom izmjerite otklon diska stražnje kočnice na točki 10 mm (0,39 in) unutar njegovog ruba. Ako je neispravan, popravite ili zamijenite disk stražnje kočnice.
</ptxt>
<spec-sdm>
<sdm-title>
Otklon diska stražnje kočnice
</sdm-title>
<sdm1>
<sdm-condition>
Granica
</sdm-condition>
<sdm-value>
0,10 mm (0,004 in)
</sdm-value>
</sdm1>
</spec-sdm>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L4C002">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09900-20607">
09900-20607
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L4C003">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09900-20701">
09900-20701
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A430009.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "65.936mm" ver = "02" gw = "137" gh = "170"/>
</figure>
<ptxt>
Mikrometrom izmjerite debljinu diska stražnje kočnice. Ako je debljina manja od granične, zamijenite disk stražnje kočnice.
</ptxt>
<spec-sdm>
<sdm-title>
Debljina diska stražnje kočnice
</sdm-title>
<sdm-part>
“a”
</sdm-part>
<sdm1>
<sdm-condition>
Standardna
</sdm-condition>
<sdm-value>
9 mm (0,35 in)
</sdm-value>
</sdm1>
<sdm1>
<sdm-condition>
Granica
</sdm-condition>
<sdm-value>
8 mm (0,31 in)
</sdm-value>
</sdm1>
</spec-sdm>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A430010.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "42.331mm" ver = "01" gw = "120" gh = "103"/>
</figure>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
